thread.title: Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win

title: Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win
text:
> Texas Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win Houston Astros' Jason Castro (15) hits a two-run single as Kansas City Royals catcher Salvador Perez, right, reaches for the pitch during the fifth inning in Game 3 of baseball's American League Division Series Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Houston. Luis Valbuena and Chris Carter scored on Castro's hit. (AP Photo/Patric Schneider)
